 S(n,m)=\sqrt{n+\sqrt{n+1+\sqrt{n+2+\dots+\sqrt{m-1+\sqrt{m}}}}}\tag{1} 
 \sqrt{n+x}-\sqrt{n}=\frac{x}{\sqrt{n+x}+\sqrt{n}}\tag{2} 
 \begin{align} S(n,m) &=\sqrt{n+S(n+1,m)}\\[6pt] &=\sqrt{n}+\frac{S(n+1,m)}{\sqrt{n+S(n+1,m)}+\sqrt{n}}\\ &\le\sqrt{n}+\frac{\sqrt{n+1}+1}{\sqrt{n+1}+1}\\[9pt] &=\sqrt{n}+1\tag{3} \end{align} 
